   "why": "Payroll-weighted blend of each Riverhead bargaining unit's own 2027 terms: CSEA gets its contractual 2.5% (2026\u20132029 CBA). PBA and SOA are between contracts \u2014 both 2023\u20132026 agreements expire 12/31/2026 with no successor yet public \u2014 so each uses its own trailing average annual raise as a placeholder. Non-union staff use a general 3.0% trend assumption. Weighted by each group's share of 2025 actual Town payroll. Full breakdown below."
